{"tid":611024,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"(多圖整合)各位借刀既巴打 唔好好似呢位巴打咁蠢","createTime":"2018-03-30T14:12:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-01T17:37:42.000Z","uid":76293,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7af607213f5c0ccf646b029e24222d4946e88558","tid":611024,"uid":76293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T14:12:00.000Z","msg":"[兩難] 屌左定屌右？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/607346/page/15?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/607346/page/15?ref=ios</a><br />\n(多圖)各位起人底既巴打 唔好好似呢位巴打咁蠢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/610661/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/610661/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n成件事有4條友:<br />\nA:holly4#169389 第一個po借刀,仲挑釁連登仔起佢IG<br />\nB:ABCDCBA#149773 第一個PO起左A底之後被C起底<br />\nC:你好好好好好野#172686 第二個PO起左B起,但實質係借刀<br />\nD:毒撚唔好咁有自信#151909 個個post都食花生推post<br />\n<br />\n第一個post:<br />\n事源第一個PO樓主(holly4)自爆(借刀)<br />\n有個巴打(ABCDCBA)就PO左第一個PO既樓主出黎<br />\n<br />\n第二個post:<br />\n點知有另一個巴打(你好好好好好野)就話自己識小小電腦 識del左個blur<br />\n於是起左(ABCDCBA)底<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/30/220248_eb21894570a41d2a85fcecd274a15d0e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F30%2F220248_eb21894570a41d2a85fcecd274a15d0e.png&h=8b255a6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲有條友係咁推post(毒撚唔好咁有自信#151909)<br />\n<br />\n但係根本就冇得咁做,張圖係(ABCDCBA#149773)手機edit blur之前既記錄只係得佢本人部手機有<br />\n<br />\n成件事就係有人係個借刀post到借刀,<br />\n扮自己識電腦技術起番人底,實質就係借刀,<br />\n但係點解ABCDCBA 開既post同佢被人起底既相咁脗合?<br />\n原因可能係:<br />\nA:有人識得ABCDCBA,知佢連登AC,之後借刀推佢出黎受死<br />\nB:ABCDCBA成個AC都係有人鋪路到今日借上借刀<br />\n<br />\n點解家下D00後借刀技術咁廢?<br />\n仲好意思話自己識少少電腦?<br />\n個post(第二個)仲呃到咁多正評?<br />\n<br />\n證明左一樣野<br />\n連登仔好多都好垃圾,好容易被利用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fc83e55ec535dd2b1b67caeacc084e60b8e1a95","tid":611024,"uid":76293,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T14:22:08.000Z","msg":"垃圾連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba5b1169b46f3f157403cdddd33d5f99db4c2768","tid":611024,"uid":76293,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T15:01:28.000Z","msg":"話緊你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2156efe80c0167f3b35040a29ee77382a7aabff6","tid":611024,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T15:14:51.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e373f26df8ef642677495a10bb54b2c61848275","tid":611024,"uid":76293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T15:32:26.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22a3ff42494f83e7d85054de4cd5a96445dd3fbd","tid":611024,"uid":76293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T16:25:19.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"9c69cf25173f455bdf1650855ee8e3bb1afc2b17","tid":611024,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T16:26:26.000Z","msg":"老A同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f74a7c97db3b1ad43cc9e40b53a92dc89c3dc5e","tid":611024,"uid":176166,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T16:27:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"02efc565c5bed0cfea0c0522d6a68a3df4aee1bd","tid":611024,"uid":76293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f74a7c97db3b1ad43cc9e40b53a92dc89c3dc5e","tid":611024,"uid":176166,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T16:27:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T17:29:43.000Z","msg":"00後係連登既毒瘤"},{"pid":"4438a927fa9d15e65d4619d81b9e841529aedd14","tid":611024,"uid":176166,"like":0,"dislik